      • add

        T add(T newEntry)
        Adds a new entry to this tree, if it does not match an existing object in the tree. Otherwise, replaces the existing object with the new entry.
        Parameters:
        newEntry - An object to be added to the tree.
        Returns:
        Either null if newEntry was not in the tree already, or the existing entry that matched the parameter newEntry and has been replaced in the tree.
